n of technology catalogues and exhibition services in the promotional merchandising and printing sectors the company provides technology services specializing in cloud and server based software its technologo offers a range of interactive image solutions which are used for increasing engagement from online businesstobusiness bb and businesstoconsumer bc buyers and reduced cart abandonment rates it also provides a website solution for companies in the promotional product industry it publishes catalogues annually for the promotional products industry which include spectrum and envoy it also hosts the promotional product roadshows more from reuters » officers and directors richard sowerby executive chairman of the board sanjay lobo managing director victoria ann robinson group managing director age  martin roy varley group commercial director director age  peter john hallett nonexecutive director age  full list on reuters » google finance beta available in hong kong  canada  us  china  ukinformation is provided as is and solely for informational purposes not for trading purposes or advice and may be delayedto see all exchange delays please see disclaimer google  google home  blog  help  report a problem  privacy policy  terms of service about altitude group plc – altitudeplccom skip to content about altitude group plc altitude group plc is the leading provider of technology and information services to the promotional products print and clothing industries which operates brands that provide information data and enterprise level technology through a software as a service “saas” model customer focus software ltd uk customer focus provides key marketing and technology tools on an international scale to both suppliers and distributors operating in the promotional merchandise industry catering to over  customers in over  countries customer focus specialises in media marketing and technology solutions for the development of the promotional product and print industries offering a market leading and internationally acclaimed collection of technology tools and marketing  publishing services designed to help grow sales and profits of promotional product suppliers distributors these tools include exhibitions catalogues search portals magazines websites and business management software the head office is currently located in manchester along with a full technical support team in sheffield uk customer focus inc usa customer focus inc provides a range of cloudbased ecommerce enterprise resource planning customer relationship management and webbased solutions to both suppliers and distributors operating in the promotional merchandise industry with sales development and support staff based in costa mesa california they deliver one system to manage all of your key business processes reducing key strokes improving customer service and cutting costs customer focus inc also provides information services to the industry including product data flow between suppliers and independent distributors working with leading us distributors since  to help reduce costs win more orders and improve their customer service customer focus enterprise customer focus enterprise is our enterprise resource planning erp software for larger promotional product distributors and suppliers and print brokers and managers since  hundreds of customers and thousands of users in the uk europe and usa have invested in customer focus enterprise gaining a highly comprehensive and robust business management system complete with integrated web stores and punchout capabilities the head office is in sheffield england along with an additional office in the usa the development support teams are based in the uk customer focus interactive imaging as the leading global provider of virtual sample technology technologo is trusted by leading manufacturers suppliers and distributors of promotional products around the world with over  years of software development and innovation at its core technologo has created a wide range of interactive image solutions that are proven to drive increased engagement from online bb and bc buyers reduced cart abandonment rates and increased average order values as part of the customer focus interactive imaging division technologo integrates seamlessly with artworktool the patented artwork creation and sharing solution increasing operational efficiency alongside the improved customer experience that benefits users in  countries who collectively create more than one million virtual samples each month our dedicated and talented team comprises of photographers graphic artists and software engineers that are focused on creating the most user friendly easytouse device agnostic image management solutions available accessible from any browser on any platform altitude group plc home our group our strategy the board corporate responsibility services investors share price financial calendar reports and presentations corporate governance rule  advisors and registrars email alerts careers contact   altitude group plc altitude group plc is the leading provider of technology and information services to the promotional products print and clothing industries which operates under the customer focus brand customer focus provides key marketing and technology tools on an international scale to both suppliers and distributors operating in the promotional merchandise industry read more technology services altitude group plc provide innovative cloud and server based software catering for companies of any size from our customer focus basic package to the more in depth enterprise solution suppliers and distributors alike can find the most suitable package to make their company function efficiently in todays business world information services altitude group plc provides the most comprehensive information service solution in the promotional merchandise industry improving data flow between suppliers and distributors and supplying them with effective mark