matically registering them for a free artworktool account and the ability to easily upgrade their access to pay for premium services such as image and vector file downloads on a per action basis“this is an exciting development which demonstrates that our patented artworktool software is globally scalable” said richard sowerby executive chairman of altitude group plc “being integrated into the primary product offering of a global brand leader serving smes around the world will drive substantial numbers of users to our artworktool platform and provide them with the opportunity to upgrade to our premium value added services” altitude group plc results login register lost password altitude group plc results homepageall newsaltitude group plc results the final results from altitude group plc have been published the group operates in the uk  usa and consists of trade only now rebranded as customer focus trade only show now rebranded as promotional product expo promoserve and ppd magazine the principal highlights of the year were • revenue up  • loss before tax of £m before share based payment charges  £m • net cash at  december  of £m  £m • successful embedding of the new management structure and processes turnover for  was £ it was also announced that martin varley will step down from the board of altitude group plc from  april  during the year the management buyout sale of the promotional marketing division dowlis ross and adproducts was completed with a final payment made of £m in cash to read full results please click here   written by victoria walton view all posts by victoria walton no comments yet leave a comment click here to cancel reply you must be logged in to post a comment events calendar plan your year with our interactive calendar view more events product news what’s hot and what’s not view more product news special offers great offers on great products view more special offers altitude group plc altlse profile  ftcom subscribe sign in menu search financial